        <briefdescription>
<para>Send OTA Success event message to firmware update control task. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The function defines the JSON string with the OTA Success event, request a message from message pool, set message type to eFwDlSuccess, set eFwUpd as sender, copy the JSON string in the message payload, retrieve a pointer to the mailbox of the firmware update control task and send message to firmware update control task&apos;s mailbox. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
