    <briefdescription>
<para>Firmware update task class derived from task base class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The firmware update task implements the interface to the FOTA download library. It starts the download process and receives the FOTA download event. It provides a callback function to receive and process the FOTA events, a function to start the download process and functions to call on download success and download failure. Furthermore two setter functions to set the name of the host, which is the server to download from and name of the binary file to be downloaded.<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Receive<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>FOTA download events via callback function</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Firmware update control task</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transmit<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Firmware update control task </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
